{"id": 29243, "name": "Bali (Anthropology)", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Bali_Anthropology_?f_ri=221567", "nofollow": false}]}, {"id": 5137263, "title": "Embodiment, Balinese Dance Theatre and the Ethnographer's Predicament", "created_at": "2013-11-18T00:21:05.285-08:00", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/5137263/Embodiment_Balinese_Dance_Theatre_and_the_Ethnographers_Predicament?f_ri=221567", "dom_id": "work_5137263", "summary": null, "downloadable_attachments": [{"id": 32339490, "asset_id": 5137263, "asset_type": "Work", "always_allow_download": false}], "ordered_authors": [{"id": 6925295, "first_name": "Jane", "last_name": "Turner", "domain_name": "mmu", "page_name": "JaneTurner", "display_name": "Jane  Turner", "profile_url": "https://mmu.academia.edu/JaneTurner?f_ri=221567", "photo": "/images/s65_no_pic.png"}], "research_interests": [{"id": 767, "name": "Anthropology", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Anthropology?f_ri=221567", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 945, "name": "Performing Arts", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Performing_Arts?f_ri=221567", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 947, "name": "Theatre Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Theatre_Studies?f_ri=221567", "nofollow": false}]}, {"id": 904228, "title": "Getting the Story Straight? Some Untimely Thoughts on History, Literature and the Performing Arts in Bali", "created_at": "2011-09-10T22:57:34.929-07:00", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/904228/Getting_the_Story_Straight_Some_Untimely_Thoughts_on_History_Literature_and_the_Performing_Arts_in_Bali?f_ri=221567", "dom_id": "work_904228", "summary": "Sudah cukup jelas bahwa ada hubungan mendalam antara seni pertunjukan dan kesusastraan Bali. Yang mungkin masih kurang jelas adalah karakter dari hubungan tersebut. Para penulis akademis maupun nonakademis seringkali menekankan pentingnya sastra kuno India dan cerita babad untuk lakon wayang kulit, arja, tope\u0301ng dan lain sebagainya. Walaupun ahli seni pertunjukan dari luar negeri kerapkali menekankan pentingnya sastra kuno, di mana sebenarnya mereka tidak mempunyai latar belakang yang kuat di bidang bahasa lokal dan sastra kuno, mereka jarang sekali mengomentari masalah seni pertunjukan. Memang ada beberapa pengecualian yang penting. Akan tetapi, pada umumnya, itulah keadaan yang terjadi sekarang di bidang studi seni pertunjukan. Artikel ini menggunakan contoh dari sebuah pertunjukan tope\u0301ng pajegan untuk menyarankan bahwa kita perlu memperhatikan sejarah, bahasa dan sastra lokal secara lebih bernuansa. Pendekatan seperti ini mungkin akan lebih sensitif terhadap sisi politik\u2014baik dari seni pertunjukan Bali maupun dari proses pengajarannya.", "downloadable_attachments": [{"id": 5462269, "asset_id": 904228, "asset_type": "Work", "always_allow_download": false}], "ordered_authors": [{"id": 228845, "first_name": "Richard", "last_name": "Fox", "domain_name": "uvic", "page_name": "RichardFox", "display_name": "Richard Fox", "profile_url": "https://uvic.academia.edu/RichardFox?f_ri=221567", "photo": "https://0.academia-photos.com/228845/50875/19216727/s65_richard.fox.jpg"}], "research_interests": [{"id": 767, "name": "Anthropology", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Anthropology?f_ri=221567", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 947, "name": "Theatre Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Theatre_Studies?f_ri=221567", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1031, "name": "Southeast Asian Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Southeast_Asian_Studies?f_ri=221567", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 2059, "name": "History of Religion", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/History_of_Religion?f_ri=221567", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 2337, "name": "Performance Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Performance_Studies?f_ri=221567"}, {"id": 4707, "name": "Indonesian Studies", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Indonesian_Studies?f_ri=221567"}, {"id": 221567, "n